---
import ColorBar from "../../components/ColorBar.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const sizeGuide = [
  { size: "S", width: "48 cm", length: "69 cm" },
  { size: "M", width: "50 cm", length: "71 cm" },
  { size: "L", width: "52 cm", length: "73 cm" },
  { size: "XL", width: "54 cm", length: "75 cm" },
  { size: "XXL", width: "56 cm", length: "77 cm" },
];
---

<Layout
  title="Guía de Tallas | Bloom Fitness Shop"
  description="Consulta nuestra guía de tallas para elegir la prenda que mejor se adapte a ti. Medidas detalladas de nuestras camisetas unisex."
  keywords="guía de tallas, medidas camisetas, tallaje ropa, bloom fitness shop"
>
  <Header />

  <main class="min-h-screen bg-black pt-12 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <nav class="flex mb-8" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol
          class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500"
        >
          <li>
            <a
              href="/tienda"
              class="hover:text-[var(--color-orange-strong)] transition-colors"
              >Tienda</a
            >
          </li>
          <li><span class="mx-2">/</span></li>
          <li class="text-[var(--color-orange-strong)] font-bold">
            Guía de Tallas
          </li>
        </ol>
      </nav>

      <h1
        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white uppercase mb-8"
      >
        Guía de <span class="text-[var(--color-orange-strong)]">Tallas</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none mb-12">
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Nuestras prendas están diseñadas para ofrecerte la máxima comodidad
          durante tus entrenamientos y en tu día a día. Para asegurar un ajuste
          perfecto, te recomendamos medir una de tus camisetas favoritas y
          comparar las medidas con nuestra tabla.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl"
      >
        <table class="w-full text-left text-white border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-zinc-800 border-b border-zinc-700">
              <th class="px-6 py-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm"
                >Talla</th
              >
              <th class="px-6 py-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm"
                >Ancho (A)</th
              >
              <th class="px-6 py-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm"
                >Largo (B)</th
              >
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-800">
            {
              sizeGuide.map((item) => (
                <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50 transition-colors">
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 font-bold text-[var(--color-orange-strong)]">
                    {item.size}
                  </td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-300">{item.width}</td>
                  <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-300">{item.length}</td>
                </tr>
              ))
            }
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div
          class="bg-zinc-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 border-dashed"
        >
          <h3
            class="text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-wide mb-4 flex items-center gap-2"
          >
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[var(--color-orange-strong)] rounded-full"
            ></span>
            ¿Cómo medir?
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span
                class="font-bold text-[var(--color-orange-strong)] whitespace-nowrap"
                >Ancho:</span
              >
              <span
                >Mide de sisa a sisa (un centímetro por debajo de las mangas).</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span
                class="font-bold text-[var(--color-orange-strong)] whitespace-nowrap"
                >Largo:</span
              >
              <span
                >Mide desde el punto más alto del hombro hasta el borde
                inferior.</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div
          class="text-center p-6 bg-[var(--color-orange-strong)]/5 rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-orange-strong)]/20 flex items-center justify-center"
        >
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm italic">
            * Las medidas son aproximadas y pueden variar ±1-2 cm según la
            fabricación. Todas las tallas son unisex.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <a
          href="/tienda"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:text-[var(--color-orange-strong)] transition-colors group"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="20"
            height="20"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-1"
            ><path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6"></path></svg
          >
          Volver a la Tienda
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <ColorBar loading="lazy" />
  <Footer />
</Layout>
